quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,1,(alr) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt
  12,2,"'iinaa 'anzalna hdha alquran bilughat alerb, laealakum -ayha alerb- taeqilun meanyh wtfhmwnha, wtemlwn bhdyh"
  12,3,"nhn nqss ealayk -ayha alrswl- 'ahsan alqasas bwhyna 'iilayk hdha alqran, wa'iin kunt qabl 'inzalh ealayk lamin alghafilin ean hadhih alakhbar, la tadri eanha shyyana"
  12,4,"adhkr -ayha alrswl- lqwmk qawl yusif labyh: 'iiniy ra'ayt fi almanam ahd eshr kwkbana, walshams walqamar ra'aytuhum li sajdyn. fakanat hadhih alruwya bshra lima wasal 'iilayh yusif ealayh alslam min elww almnzlt fi aldunya walakhrt"
  12,5,"qal yaequb liaibnih ywsf: ya bunaya la tudhkar l'ikhwtk hadhih alruwya fyhsdwk, wyeadwk, wyhtalu fi 'ihlakk, 'iina alshaytan lil'iinsan eaduun zahir aledawt"
  12,6,"wkma 'arak rabik hadhih alruwya fkdhlk ystfyk wayuealimuk tafsir ma yarah alnaas fi mnamhm min alruwaa mimaa twwl 'iilayh waqeana, wayutimu niematah ealayk waealaa al yaequb balnbwt walrsalt, kama 'atamaha min qibal ealaa 'abawayk 'iibrahim wa'iishaq balnbwt walrsal. 'iina rabak ealim biman ystfyh min ebadh, hakim fi tadbir 'umur khlqh"